{"tid":1632230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家搞清楚，人權法先係主線，唔好比人spin","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T16:05:22.000Z","uid":38744,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c1855ff7d1e7c3af60ce2fa3ab4d68f28c29a077","tid":1632230,"uid":38744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0361a154447376cc32a0f5b78f31c89930fa9b3c","tid":1632230,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:21:21.000Z","msg":"推俾外國旅客 咪俾黨鐵賺錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632118\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632118</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"011ded9f2377e6d53ab33f374f8b70b6b3a0301b","tid":1632230,"uid":38744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:21:47.000Z","msg":"唔好迷失"},{"pid":"7e784952a07dc5d2810c301ed890a3f2fcc20a21","tid":1632230,"uid":68896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:59.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n主線任務：人權法通過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n神獸裝飾任只係突發side quest<br />\n<br />\n主線任有限時唔搞掂好難再推進劇情"},{"pid":"a2ca3ec5985f4b8e64123ef484418a333ce560fb","tid":1632230,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:26:08.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 10.7 爆食日 攪珠結果出爐<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632126</a>"},{"pid":"1b6b787dc6874d36d3d8cfcd2f95bfad08362196","tid":1632230,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:26:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"c4a641c9d1c6538c395f73679cf4bea3796ca609","tid":1632230,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:26:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家太過focus係蒙面法 裝修 私了 忽略左緊急法帶來既經濟危機 大家要明白呢一點 呢個係港共最大春袋</span></span>"},{"pid":"e6c2ba9f91da07a595a3f6fb345f25a073856baf","tid":1632230,"uid":169074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:27:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2fbb4ac980c2a67fbc52e82a470fd80020f545d","tid":1632230,"uid":296533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:27:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人權法案先係主線！！</span></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"bac7b7b5669448b0c53c30bdc33c3cc3d7d87470","tid":1632230,"uid":68896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:28:24.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"60f1101d2af0802706aa359ccdd233510061ca2d","tid":1632230,"uid":68896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:28:36.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"bf24d59c673d6507ea231d83bcbbe4fb80abf09e","tid":1632230,"uid":68896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:28:50.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"624694134fef502de4ed3f8341ebf0ffeb3fc3f7","tid":1632230,"uid":68896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:29:02.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"9d051ac110bc72d1bbd1f16d65fa70790f1b32ee","tid":1632230,"uid":68896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:29:12.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"bf79ac543148cd8afeea7f314cbafc212762dff3","tid":1632230,"uid":68896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:29:54.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"371a007d4094cdeb575947bec65d081b9ecba537","tid":1632230,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:30:20.000Z","msg":"蒙面法前後戴口罩嘅意義唔同咗 而依個意義應該決定我地嘅行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630541\" data-auto-link t